%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%
flowchart LR
    U[User / Browser / Mobile]
    MFA[MFA Verification<br/>Authenticator / OTP / Push]
    IDP[Identity Provider<br/>OIDC / OAuth2 / SSO]
    CDN[CDN<br/>HTTPS + TLS 1.2/1.3]
    DDoS[DDoS Protection<br/>AWS Shield / Edge Protection]
    WAF[WAF<br/>L7 Filtering]
    FW[Firewall / Security Policy Layer<br/>IP Filtering / Allow-Deny Rules]
    IPS[IDS / IPS<br/>Threat Detection / Intrusion Prevention]
    LB[Reverse Proxy / Load Balancer<br/>HTTPS + TLS]
    GW[API Gateway<br/>HTTPS + TLS<br/>OAuth2 / JWT Validation]
    BFF[BFF Layer<br/>HTTPS / gRPC + TLS<br/>JWT Validation]
    ORCH[Journey Orchestrator<br/>REST / gRPC + TLS / mTLS]
    MS[Biz Microservices<br/>REST / gRPC + mTLS<br/>RBAC + ABAC]
    CACHE[Redis Cache<br/>TLS-enabled Redis Protocol]
    DB[(RDS / NoSQL / Vector DB<br/>TLS + Encryption at Rest)]
    DOC[S3 / Document Store<br/>HTTPS + SSE-KMS]
    EVT[Event Platform<br/>Kafka / AMQP + TLS / mTLS]
    INT[Integration Layer<br/>HTTPS + OAuth2 / API Keys]
    AI[AI Orchestrator<br/>HTTPS + TLS + Policy Controls]
    GEN[GenAI / LLM<br/>HTTPS + TLS]
    MON[Monitoring / SIEM / Security Ops<br/>TLS]
    SEC[Secrets / KMS / IAM<br/>Key & Credential Control]

    U -->|Login Request<br/>HTTPS + TLS| IDP
    IDP -->|MFA Challenge| MFA
    MFA -->|MFA Success| IDP
    IDP -->|JWT Token Issued| U

    U -->|HTTPS + TLS| CDN
    CDN -->|HTTPS + TLS| DDoS
    DDoS -->|Scrubbed Traffic| WAF
    WAF -->|Filtered Traffic| FW
    FW -->|Allowed Traffic| IPS
    IPS -->|Inspected Traffic| LB
    LB -->|HTTPS + TLS| GW

    GW -->|HTTPS + TLS + JWT| BFF
    BFF -->|HTTPS / gRPC + TLS + JWT| ORCH
    BFF -->|HTTPS / gRPC + TLS + JWT| MS
    BFF -->|TLS Redis| CACHE

    ORCH -->|mTLS + Service Auth| MS
    MS -->|TLS + DB Auth| DB
    MS -->|HTTPS + IAM / Signed URL| DOC
    MS -->|Kafka / AMQP + TLS / mTLS| EVT
    MS -->|HTTPS + TLS + OAuth2 / API Key| INT

    BFF -->|HTTPS + TLS + JWT| AI
    AI -->|HTTPS + TLS| GEN
    AI -->|TLS + Auth| DB

    SEC --- GW
    SEC --- BFF
    SEC --- MS
    SEC --- DB
    SEC --- DOC
    SEC --- AI

    GW -->|TLS Logs| MON
    BFF -->|TLS Logs| MON
    ORCH -->|TLS Logs| MON
    MS -->|TLS Logs| MON
    IPS -->|Security Events| MON
    WAF -->|Threat Logs| MON
    FW -->|Access Logs| MON